This Repo houses a demo implementation of the Fidel Attack method to Recreate sample data from weight updates in CNN and FCNN networks.

The details of the Fidel attack method are discussed in detail in the paper: 
Fidel: Reconstructing Private Training Samples from Weight Updates in Federated Learning
By David Enthoven and Zaid Al-Ars
Pre-print availible here http://arxiv-export-lb.library.cornell.edu/pdf/2101.00159
